race.comment: BEST NAN (1) produced a moderate performance last time when seventh at Gunnedah over 340m behind Coco Mac (20.34) in a Grade 4/5. Placed at her previous run. Form from her last run is proving strong. Has ability and is a key runner. RAZZLE ANN (8) produced a modest effort most recently when sixth at this track over 330m behind Nangar Archie (19.35) in a Mix 1/2/3. Has ability and can atone. JUST STOP IT (2) had a tricky draw last time and although midfield in fourth wasn't far away finishing 3.5 lengths from the winner (19.12). Should be about the money. WHAT'S THAT PAL (7) is right in the mix.
